{"tid":1029671,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王祖藍誠意爆燈 謝票謝足125場","createTime":"2019-02-20T11:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T11:53:02.000Z","uid":160973,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"849e8fefa502a44951e86b361a86943d18ae7bcd","tid":1029671,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"王祖藍首次執導的電影《你咪理，我愛你！》喺2019農曆新年檔期上畫，電影上映兩個多星期票房已達900萬的佳績。祖藍為了答謝觀眾的熱烈支持，由正式上畫當天（1月31日）便展開港九新界謝票之旅，瘋狂謝票謝足125場，誠意絕對爆晒燈。<br />\n<br />\n唔少入場支持電影嘅觀眾見到祖藍真人都表示驚喜，網民更大讚呢位導演熱血得嚟又有heart。而問到祖藍點解要咁辛苦跑勻港九新界戲院謝票，他笑說：「咁話晒係第一次做導演，都知自己有好多不足嘅地方，所以都好想喺戲院度問吓觀眾嘅第一身意見，希望之後盡量改善。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tyXx4F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tyXx4F&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n82mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=46e1b750\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tyXx4F</a>"},{"pid":"dc4e0716f4c49bb855f6e7677a43980239f76b91","tid":1029671,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"成廿日都未夠一千個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611fe092949a45d007a06f72cc63c979504d0d46","tid":1029671,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecedbca216b47e3a44faf955f9a8b1ece1422fd","tid":1029671,"uid":62384,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"見到佢個名已經唔想睇"},{"pid":"b26fba653625535b5c59e117e4e3d0267c5e8769","tid":1029671,"uid":50196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eecedbca216b47e3a44faf955f9a8b1ece1422fd","tid":1029671,"uid":62384,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"見到佢個名已經唔想睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"蝗蛆蝻"},{"pid":"e974036b